posting_body: ['LAUNDRY IN UNIT / HOTEL AMENETIES / FITNESS CENTER / CONCIERGE / GARAGE', 'Listing ID #: 211095', 'Price: $8,678', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 2.0', 'Bathrooms: 2.0', 'Building Amenities', 'Bicycle Room', 'Laundry', 'Lounge', 'New Construction', 'Subway', 'Come home to concierge and lifestyle services inspired by the world’s finest hotels and resorts and unparalleled amenities, right where you live.', 'This unbelievable apartment boasts of the finest finishes and appointments.', 'This rare and unique find will make you want to work from home permanently.', "Don't miss the opportunity to live in a great work of art.", 'One of the Tallest Residential Towers in North America by one of the most acclaimed architects of our time.', 'Throughout the 6th, 7th, and 8th floors, residents have exclusive access to 22,000 square feet of indoor and outdoor health, wellness, social, and entertainment amenity spaces.', 'These amenities, together with an extensive range of concierge and lifestyle services, offer residents an experience found only in world-class hotels and resorts.', "Tribeca is a phenomenal neighborhood featuring upscale restaurants and boutiques that make up it's chic commercial center, while quiet cobblestone streets and impressive loft buildings lend the area an air of tranquility.", 'For showings contact: Adel Talebpour / Bouklis Group / 212-961-7334 (Cell) / <URL> / <URL> / <URL>', 'Adel Talebpour', 'Phone: 212-402-7855', 'Mobile: 212-961-7334', 'Email: <URL>', 'The Bouklis Group \xa0 212-402-7855 \xa0 212-961-7334 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Adel Talebpour at 212-961-7334']
